      "name": "Hemolysis Index Benchmark Comparison",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) against in-vitro measurements from the FDA benchmark dataset across five operating points. Mean relative error 18.4%; all predictions within 25% of measured values. Validation performed at MRL 5 conditions.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/hemolysis-validation-run"
    },
